R. W. ROBBERSON v. Minnie M. RICHARDS. No. 7236. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. May 14, 1963. C. J. Watts, Oklahoma City, Okl., and Clark Y. Owens, Wichita, Kan., for appellant. Malcolm Miller, Wichita, Kan., for ap-pellee.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and PICKETT and LEWIS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed May 14, 1963, on motion of appellant.
